| Case | Keyword Used  | Calls Constructor Of | Purpose                                       |
| ---- | ------------- | -------------------- | --------------------------------------------- |
| 1    | `super()`     | Superclass           | Calls default constructor                     |
| 2    | `super(args)` | Superclass           | Calls parameterized constructor               |
| 3    | `this()`      | Same class           | Calls default constructor of same class       |
| 4    | `this(args)`  | Same class           | Calls parameterized constructor of same class |


